description:
Elimin8™ is a simple addictive number based Brain teaser. Drop numbered boxes on the board and eliminate the existing boxes. The boxes disappear whenever the number on a box matches the size of the row or column that box is in. 

With 4 Addictive gameplay modes and 6 unique powerups, this game will keep you coming back day after day. Are you game for some Elimin8ion?

FEATURES 
•4 addictive game modes Classic, Survival, Time Rush and Elimin8r
•6 Unique Powerups
•80 mind boggling puzzles in the Elimin8r mode
•Game Center and Openfeint Support
•Leaderboards & Achievements 
•Great Graphics and soothing music

Game Modes:
Classic: The basic game, all you need to do is drop boxes, difficulty increases as you go on.
Elimin8r: The objective of this mode is eliminating all the flashing boxes present on the board
Time Rush: Timed mode which requires quick reflexes and strategy, difficulty increases as time flies by. 
Survival: This mode needs strategy and speed, in this mode you need to survive for as many levels as you can.

If you like the game, please rate it 5 stars (★★★★★).
